claim.claim-text:
1. A method of making solid state image pickup device, the method comprising:
forming a peripheral circuit region and a pixel region in a semiconductor substrate, the pixel region including a photo-electric conversion device and a pixel;
forming a wiring layer over a first surface side of the semiconductor substrate, the first surface being opposite to a light receiving surface of the semiconductor substrate;
forming a light-shielding film over the light receiving surface, the light-shielding film covering the peripheral circuit region and the pixel;
forming an opening through the light-shielding film, the opening being formed over the photo-electric conversion device,
wherein the pixel is configured to detect black level in the pixel region, the opening not being formed over the pixel.
